Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质问者型 似乎将目标转移到飞龙上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都再三叮嘱他们不要搭理新联合国的机体了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是救下他们 之后可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α线 138-177步完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,β线全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布伦希尔德系统部分 全部就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 移除固定锚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.33,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(806,1000)}Dux Stopper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们也进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学他们怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战内容我没必要向你们说明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你平时不是都会回答的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是学校！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里派出的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是从API-1来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛现在将开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿岸一带的居民请小心巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巡航启动最终进程 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外缘部附属部件固定于各部位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并发出解除警报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用于确保资源的红莲岛 今天也就功成身退了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲岛 解除完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开单独的重力波防护罩后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将开始发送伪装信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.75,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(856,1000)}dummy beacon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来让红莲岛作为诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航行系统已确认正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布伦希尔德系统 正常运行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外缘部固定轴 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.15,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(892,1000)}purge
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要离开这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巡航进程全部完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎发动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎发动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎内压力上升
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1至第5引擎 无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲岛 分离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各连结处 无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巡航速度维持在5
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 海流控制等级固定在7
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制等级 固定在7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒区域扩大到外围200单位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拍摄这部机体的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它又想来同化我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然连这种装备都有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好惊讶的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是救了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙在龙宫岛航线上展开了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话 5分钟后将到达第二防卫圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要老师 能改变航向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要花上半天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不破坏内核就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我扔过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认本岛被击中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 总比岛被破坏要好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伪装镜面解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力波防护罩展开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传 传来了…歌声…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这歌声是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在唱歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道该怎么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质问者型 已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是完全醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岛是…这地方原来有岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:17:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地图上没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,17区侦察机 Youngstar-2呼叫新联合国总部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Youngstar-2已发现API-1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Youngstar-2已发现API-1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能着陆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是掉下来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么无视命令 搭救了新联合国的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救人是错的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…有时候是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是觉得我很天真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊 战果丰硕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 能活着回来就比什么都强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是这样我就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了 还有训练要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要是不赶紧像你们这样派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被赶出岛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说我们战果丰硕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是岛上的战斗机救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑和总士的战斗好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后出来了一个很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了很厉害的事 真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也去找狩谷老师看看战斗录像呗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看了我可能就会没自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Youngstar-2发出讯息的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算找到巨人之岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会以这种形式迎来这一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻能够开动古船的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是新的水手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到新航路的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是纯真的船员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯真的我们找到的航海图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是从天上掉落的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通向苦难的道路
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出航的龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知要前往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到未来的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然被迫迈出新的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时 他们进行了言语的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 苍穹的法芙娜 第五回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定 -誓言-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
